description:
Create Zustand store for app state and persist repo list.

## Implementation
1. Create Zustand store for application state
2. Configure persistence to Tauri app data directory
3. Store list of added repositories

## State Shape
```typescript
interface AppState {
  repos: Repository[];
  selectedRepoId: string | null;
  addRepo: (path: string) => void;
  removeRepo: (id: string) => void;
  selectRepo: (id: string) => void;
}

interface Repository {
  id: string;
  path: string;
  name: string;
}
```

## Files to Create
- src/store/appStore.ts
- src/store/index.ts
- src/types/repository.ts

## Persistence
Use Zustand persist middleware with custom storage adapter for Tauri's app data directory (via @tauri-apps/api/path and @tauri-apps/plugin-fs)

## Acceptance Criteria
- Store works in React components
- Repos persist across app restart
- Unit tests for store actions
